
Please install SDL and opengl:
sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev

Install glew:
sudo apt-get install libglew-dev glew-utils

Install glm:
sudo apt-get install libglm-dev

Install libsdl2-image:
sudo apt-get install libsdl2-image-2.0-0 libsdl2-image-dev

https://packages.debian.org/sid/libsdl2-image-dev
https://packages.debian.org/stretch/libsdl2-image-2.0-0